description: Fabulous luxury 2 story Penthouse in newer built building near Andrew Square, Moakley Park, and Carson Beach. High end finishes throughout in this 2 bedroom, 2 bath terrific city abode. Top of the line, Sub Zero & Wolf appliances will delight the cook in you as you enjoy the open concept, and adjacent comfortable living room. Charming Master bedroom and a well equipped master bath you'd expect. Nearby second bedroom with hall bath. Roof level bonus room for home office or den with wet bar and adjoining large private roof deck oasis with views. Tremendous value in this comfortable and elegant home for the upwardly mobile savvy Buyer. Enjoy all that South Boston offers with the space, privacy, and amenities you'd expect. Open House attendees:  Buzz unit 402. Go to 4th Floor from elevator. PH2 is the unit. Across hall from elevator door.
